 privately developed liquid-fueled rocket to reach orbit.\n- **First Private Company to Reach the ISS**: In 2012, the Dragon spacecraft became the first commercial spacecraft to deliver cargo to the ISS.\n- **First Reusable Orbital Rocket**: In 2015, SpaceX successfully landed the first stage of the Falcon 9 rocket, demonstrating the feasibility of reusability.\n- **Crewed Spaceflight**: In 2020, SpaceX's Crew Dragon became the first commercial spacecraft to carry astronauts to the ISS, marking a new era in human spaceflight.\n\nOverall, SpaceX has transformed the landscape of space exploration by making it more accessible and cost-effective, paving the way for future missions to the Moon, Mars, and beyond.", additional_kwargs={'refusal': None}, response_metadata={'token_usage': {'completion_tokens': 500, 'prompt_tokens': 368, 'total_tokens': 868, 'completion_tokens_details': {'accepted_prediction_tokens': 0, 'audio_tokens': 0, 'reasoning_tokens': 0, 'rejected_prediction_tokens': 0}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'audio_tokens': 0, 'cached_tokens': 0}, 'input_tokens': 0, 'output_tokens': 0, 'input_tokens_details': None}, 'model_name': 'gpt-4o-mini', 'system_fingerprint': 'fp_eb37e061ec', 'finish_reason': 'stop', 'logprobs': None}, id='run-3e37511e-322a-4564-b776-80f23ba20186-0', usage_metadata={'input_tokens': 368, 'output_tokens': 500, 'total_tokens': 868, 'input_token_details': {'audio': 0, 'cache_read': 0}, 'output_token_details': {'audio': 0, 'reasoning': 0}})], 'is_last_step': False}
